{"tid":1975841,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"白宮聲明：G7領袖支持川普 籲WHO徹底檢討和改革","createTime":"2020-04-16T22:00:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T08:50:03.000Z","uid":28765,"like":89,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"f3e877bf92a778608d3a0a5c05d1944f66ee0660","tid":1975841,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T22:00:02.000Z","msg":"〔編譯茅毅／綜合報導〕白宮16日聲明，對於美國總統川普痛批世衛組織（WHO），七大工業國集團（G7）成員國的領袖當天均表達支持，並呼籲WHO這個聯合國專門機構，進行「徹底的檢討和改革」。<br />\n<br />\n川普與英國、加拿大、法國、德國、義大利與日本等其他G7國家的領袖，共同舉行一場視訊會議，WHO也是會中討論的內容。<br />\n<br />\n對此，白宮在該聲明中表示，其他G7成員國的領袖一致贊同、支持川普對WHO的立場、態度。該聲明強調，這些領袖認識到，G7各國每年都貢獻1億多美元給WHO。該聲明提到，這場視訊會議大多集中在討論WHO缺乏透明度以及該國際組織對造成全球大流行的武漢肺炎疫情之長期管理不善。這些領袖呼籲WHO進行徹底的檢討和改革程序。<br />\n<br />\n川普14日抨擊WHO隱匿武肺疫情在中國爆發的程度，並對北京言聽計從。美國作為WHO歲入的最大貢獻國，他已揚言中斷華府對WHO的資助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3136516\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3136516&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10FLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=73a21fa8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3136516&h=5bbd9ff7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3136516</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.foxnews.com/politics/g7-leaders-call-for-thorough-review-of-besieged-who-amid-questions-about-coronavirus-pro-china-bias\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fg7-leaders-call-for-thorough-review-of-besieged-who-amid-questions-about-coronavirus-pro-china-bias&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10FLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=30259b23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fg7-leaders-call-for-thorough-review-of-besieged-who-amid-questions-about-coronavirus-pro-china-bias&h=efed9a8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.foxnews.com/politics/g7-leaders-call-for-thorough-review-of-besieged-who-amid-questions-about-coronavi